						               													<description>Translation from back of the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The board game CONDUCTEUR aims to familiarize the players with the road safety code and the laws that govern it. The situations presented correspond to the reality that drivers and future drivers will face.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of each player is: get the least possible offense due to his negligence or imprudence for they result in the accumulation of demerit points and expensive fines . The player thus becomes well aware of the benefits of driving with vigilance and attention.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Eight (8) players can take part in the game. They receive initially a driver's license with 0 demerit points. The player who accumulates 15 demerit points will have his license revoked and will be removed from the game. Whoever ends the game with the best record will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the outset, all drivers are insured under a policy of &amp;quot;basic liability insurance&amp;quot; covering damage to their vehicle when they are the victims of an accident for which they are not responsible for, covering the damage to others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
